title: Karambit Basic Training 1 of 3 - iPod
description:
Karambit Basic Training 1 - iPod

DVD Rip to iPod

Director: Steve Tarani

In this series you will learn the traditional karambit method. The karambit can be defined as a small hand-held, curved fixed blade for personal-defense. Steve Tarani gives us an outstanding introduction to this unique and highly effective weapon. 

Guro Tarani Will Teach You:

Vol 1: Karambit is one of the most awesome personal defense weapons of the Indonesian Archipelago. This video presents the history, training methods and other requisite skills in operating the Karambit. 

Keywords: silat, escrima, kali, knife fighting, self defense, martial art
